Title: Join the army -- run an obstacle course
Put on your blue suede shoes -- dance
Hunt in the forest while dragging
Make it rain! Water your plants
Do you like Bob the Builder? Hammer some nails
Stand in the Hack Nashville registration line
Like country music? Drive a tractor
Come on, Paul Bunyan -- chop trees
Be a fan! Cheer on your favorite team
Pull out your flute and play some jazz
Find your inner Dude (he abides) -- bowl
Beat Forrest Gump -- play ping pong
Be Matthew McConaughey -- drive your Lincoln
Snow shoe across the frozen tundra
Stand on a block of ice
